<title>currentColor is inherited correctly in rgb RCS, permutation</title>
<link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-5/#resolving-rcs">
<link rel="author" href="mailto:chris@w32768.org" title="Chris Lilley"><link rel="author" href="mailto:chris@w3.org" title="Chris Lilley"><link rel="author" href="mailto:chris@w3.org" title="Chris Lilley"><link rel="author" href="mailto:chris@w32766.org" title="Chris Lilley"><link rel="author" href="mailto:chris@w3.org" title="Chris Lilley">
<style>
div {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background-color: red;
  color: yellow;
  background-color: rgb(from currentColor g r b);
}
div div {
  color: #800000;
  background-color: inherit;
}
</style>
